Clemens Marschner wrote:
> 1. I think the new document boost is missing, isn't it?
> With that it should be something like
> 
>  score_d = sum_t(tf_q * idf_t / norm_q * tf_d * idf_t / norm_d_t * boost_t)
> * coord_q_d * boost_d
